### Render Custom Bar Label - Recharts

Source: https://github.com/recharts/recharts/blob/main/storybook/stories/Customise.mdx

Displays custom labels on bar chart bars positioned at the center-top of each bar. Accepts payload, x, y, width, height, and value as destructured parameters. Returns styled text element with formatted value display.

```javascript
export const renderCustomBarLabel = ({ payload, x, y, width, height, value }) => {
  return <text x={x + width / 2} y={y} fill="#666" textAnchor="middle" dy={-6}>{`value: ${value}`}</text>;
};
```

