### Render Recharts Rectangle Component in SVG

Source: https://github.com/recharts/recharts/blob/main/storybook/stories/API/shapes/Rectangle.mdx

This code snippet demonstrates how to render a Recharts Rectangle component directly within an SVG container. It showcases essential properties like position (x, y), dimensions (height, width), and styling (stroke, fill) for customizing the rectangle's appearance. The Rectangle acts as a foundational SVG element.

```jsx
<svg height={100} width="100%">
  <Rectangle x={0} y={0} height={100} width={200} stroke="#111" fill="red" />
</svg>
```
